Configuration Reference

Config file:
  Default path: ~/.spinedigest/config.json
  Override path: SPINEDIGEST_CONFIG

Precedence:
  - Environment variables override the config file.
  - `--prompt` overrides both config and environment prompt settings for one run.
  - Explicit format flags override file-extension inference.

Minimum digest configuration:
  - llm.provider
  - llm.model
  These are required only for source digest runs.

Main config sections:
  - prompt
  - llm.provider
  - llm.model
  - llm.apiKey
  - llm.baseURL
  - llm.name
  - paths.cacheDir
  - paths.debugLogDir
  - request.concurrent
  - request.timeout
  - request.retryTimes
  - request.retryIntervalSeconds
  - request.temperature
  - request.topP
  - request.stream

Important env vars:
  SPINEDIGEST_PROMPT
  SPINEDIGEST_LLM_PROVIDER
  SPINEDIGEST_LLM_MODEL
  SPINEDIGEST_LLM_BASE_URL
  SPINEDIGEST_LLM_NAME
  SPINEDIGEST_LLM_API_KEY
  SPINEDIGEST_CACHE_DIR
  SPINEDIGEST_DEBUG_LOG_DIR
  SPINEDIGEST_REQUEST_CONCURRENT
  SPINEDIGEST_REQUEST_TIMEOUT
  SPINEDIGEST_REQUEST_RETRY_TIMES
  SPINEDIGEST_REQUEST_RETRY_INTERVAL_SECONDS
  SPINEDIGEST_REQUEST_TEMPERATURE
  SPINEDIGEST_REQUEST_TOP_P
  SPINEDIGEST_REQUEST_STREAM

Minimal config skeleton:
  {
    "llm": {
      "provider": "openai",
      "model": "gpt-4.1"
    }
  }

